WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.833 --> 00:00:05.433
A taxi driver was driving...

2
00:00:05.433 --> 00:00:08.233
and a sleepy deaf person rushed out,

3
00:00:08.233 --> 00:00:12.033
because they were late for an appointment.

4
00:00:12.033 --> 00:00:15.576
They went down the stairs,

5
00:00:15.576 --> 00:00:19.171
called an Uber,

6
00:00:19.171 --> 00:00:25.933
and the cab showed up.

7
00:00:25.933 --> 00:00:29.033
They were putting their suitcase in the car,

8
00:00:29.033 --> 00:00:32.333
and the driver asked where they were going.

9
00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:34.533
The deaf person closed the door and said:

10
00:00:34.533 --> 00:00:38.199
Oh sorry, I'm deaf!

11
00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:43.433
The driver: Where are you going?

12
00:00:43.433 --> 00:00:47.075
The deaf person motioned to keep going straight.

13
00:00:47.075 --> 00:00:50.899
The driver drove straight

14
00:00:50.900 --> 00:00:53.533
and didn't know what to do with their deaf passenger.

15
00:00:53.533 --> 00:00:59.066
They kept glancing in the rearview mirror and kept driving...

16
00:00:59.066 --> 00:01:00.999
"Now turn left"

17
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.733
"OK, left"

18
00:01:04.733 --> 00:01:07.066
They kept driving

19
00:01:07.066 --> 00:01:11.166
and stopped at the red light.

20
00:01:11.166 --> 00:01:14.599
They waited for people to cross.

21
00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:17.100
The deaf person was very anxious

22
00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:19.100
because it was already late.

23
00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:22.166
Let's go please, I'm really late!

24
00:01:22.166 --> 00:01:25.232
"Wait, it's red"

25
00:01:25.233 --> 00:01:27.766
Let's go please!

26
00:01:27.766 --> 00:01:30.899
The driver obeyed

27
00:01:30.900 --> 00:01:33.866
and ran the red light.

28
00:01:33.866 --> 00:01:38.499
The passenger, really worried about being late...

29
00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:42.800
"Hey, if you hit a red light, ignore it"

30
00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:47.900
"Just keep going, because it's really late"

31
00:01:47.900 --> 00:01:52.433
Then a patrol car showed up

32
00:01:52.433 --> 00:01:55.199
and told them to pull over.

33
00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:59.700
They pulled over and said: Hey, what happened?

34
00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:02.000
"You ran a red light"

35
00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:09.066
"Oh yeah, sorry, my passenger is deaf"

36
00:02:09.066 --> 00:02:13.599
They spoke and sure enough, the deaf person couldn't hear them.

37
00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:16.233
"All right,

38
00:02:16.233 --> 00:02:19.299
you can pay me off"

39
00:02:19.300 --> 00:02:23.233
They paid up and kept driving.

40
00:02:23.233 --> 00:02:26.166
The deaf person was desperate

41
00:02:26.166 --> 00:02:28.966
and asked to switch seats.

42
00:02:28.966 --> 00:02:34.732
The driver agreed and now the deaf person was driving.

43
00:02:34.733 --> 00:02:41.199
And they blew through every red light.

44
00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:47.266
The driver was stunned that they ran the lights.

45
00:02:47.266 --> 00:02:52.366
A cop spotted them

46
00:02:52.366 --> 00:02:54.899
and followed them for a while.

47
00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:59.433
And said: Pull over!

48
00:02:59.433 --> 00:03:03.199
So they pulled over.

49
00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:05.300
What happened?

50
00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:09.266
"Oh, I'm deaf, sorry"

51
00:03:09.266 --> 00:03:13.032
And the officer: You're fine, go ahead.

52
00:03:13.033 --> 00:03:18.433
The shocked driver: Just because they're deaf!

53
00:03:18.433 --> 00:03:23.833
They stopped me a minute ago and I had to pay a bribe!

54
00:03:23.833 --> 00:03:29.299
I'll learn!

55
00:03:29.300 --> 00:03:37.133
The deaf person got to their destination, paid the driver, and left.

56
00:03:37.133 --> 00:03:39.999
The driver learned from the experience.

57
00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:44.933
They picked up another fare and had to get somewhere fast.

58
00:03:44.933 --> 00:03:51.366
They remembered what happened with their deaf passenger.

59
00:03:51.366 --> 00:03:58.132
They took off, drove, and ran the lights.

60
00:03:58.133 --> 00:04:01.333
A cop pulled them over and they said: I'm deaf!

61
00:04:01.333 --> 00:04:03.899
The officer said: OK, wait.

62
00:04:03.900 --> 00:04:09.100
They went and got a manual and started signing to them.

63
00:04:09.100 --> 00:04:10.902
And the stunned driver: What?

64
00:04:10.902 --> 00:04:12.671
"Sorry, talk to me"

65
00:04:12.671 --> 00:04:19.621
And that's how the officer realized they could hear.
